{"type":"article","id":21186,"title":"清真组装画：香港少年大战习包子","uid":50245,"topics":[136,339,9207,17,1,163],"contents":"这是中港版的大卫vs歌利亚，各种绘图元素取自不同的彩色油画、漫画和新闻照片，经美术处理组装而成。古兰经里也提到大卫和歌利亚，把他们分别叫达伍德和查鲁特。所以这是一幅很清真的画。<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EcCXMWrUYAAWbNn?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EcCXMWrUYAAWbNn?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EcCXMWrUYAAWbNn?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-07-04","agreeCount":4,"discussionCount":0}